    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Ready to hit the road in a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle? This car is in good condition and has plenty of great miles ahead! The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only the light, everyday wear you'd expect from a regularly used car \u2014 nothing that takes away from the enjoyment of driving it. The exterior holds up nicely, and mechanically it's been well maintained. If you're looking for a solid, reliable ride at a fair price, this one is well worth a look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has significant mechanical issues that will require substantial repair work in the near term. The exterior shows heavy scratches, dents, and other cosmetic damage. The interior is worn with visible damage to seating and trim. Suitable for buyers willing to invest in repairs or looking for parts.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in good condition \u2014 it's a solid, well-maintained car that offers reliable everyday performance without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; there are no significant dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing modest signs of regular use but nothing that detracts from the driving experience. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has been properly maintained \u2014 all major systems including engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension are in good working order. Buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready to drive without needing immediate repairs, though as with any used car in this tier, some cosmetic imperfections are present. This is an honest, no-surprises listing for a buyer who wants quality and reliability at a fair market price.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and I want to give any serious buyer a complete and honest picture of what that means. This car is in exceptional, like-new condition \u2014 the kind of vehicle that is genuinely rare to find on the used market. The exterior paint is flawless, with no scratches, chips, dings, or swirl marks that you'd typically expect on a used car. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim pieces, chrome accents, and glass are in pristine shape. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells as though it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2014 the upholstery is spotless, the dashboard and door panels show no wear, and every button, knob, and screen functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in top-tier shape: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all fluids are clean and at proper levels, the brakes have excellent life remaining, and the tires are in like-new condition with deep, even tread. There are no warning lights, no unusual sounds, and no deferred maintenance items. Service records are available and up to date. If you're looking for a used car that genuinely performs and presents like a new one, this is it.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Rock-Bottom Deal on a Fixer-Upper \u2014 Grab It Before It's Gone! \ud83d\udd27\n\nSometimes the best deals come in rough packages! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 expect significant mechanical issues, visible wear, and cosmetic damage throughout. It's not a daily driver without some serious TLC, but at this price, it's a fantastic opportunity for a dedicated DIYer, a parts hunter, or someone with the skills to bring it back to life. Everything you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just an honest deal at an honest price. Come take a look and make it yours!",
      "price": 2500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This dependable vehicle presents a fantastic opportunity for the savvy buyer seeking solid, everyday reliability without the premium price tag. Showing the character of a well-loved car, it has been maintained with care and is ready to handle your daily commute or weekend adventures with confidence. The mechanicals are sound, the interior is comfortable and functional, and it drives exactly as you'd hope \u2014 smooth, responsive, and road-ready. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why this is one of the smarter buys on our lot today.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 Have I got a gem for you today! This beauty is one of those cars that just puts a smile on your face every single time you get behind the wheel. She's been well looked after and it really shows \u2014 solid mechanicals, a comfortable interior that's ready for your next adventure, and that satisfying feel of a car that's been genuinely cared for. Sure, she's got a little character from her years on the road (what well-loved car doesn't?), but nothing that gets in the way of a great drive. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just cruising around town, this one's got you covered. I'm the kind of seller who wants you to drive away happy \u2014 come take her for a spin and see for yourself. You won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Rolling in with a confidence that only comes from a well-sorted drivetrain, this machine presents as a genuinely capable daily driver with enthusiast bones. The powerplant pulls cleanly through the rev range with no hesitation or smoke at cold start or operating temp \u2014 a strong indicator of healthy piston ring seal and valve train integrity. Suspension geometry feels tight with minimal body roll, suggesting bushings and control arm hardware are in serviceable condition. Braking response is progressive and fade-resistant under repeated application. Interior shows honest wear consistent with regular use \u2014 nothing a detail session won't address. All primary electrical systems \u2014 HVAC, infotainment, windows, and lighting \u2014 function as designed. This is a driver's car that's been used as intended, not babied into fragility. Priced to move for the buyer who knows what they're looking at.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    }
  ],
